data.title: The Florencia Lozano Homepage
data.text:
Del Delgado

Téa's older brother, FBI Agent. He considers it his duty to protect Téa. Her closest familial tie.

Abuela

Abuela is Téa's grandmother.

Todd Manning

Téa's husband, most 'infamous' client, and soulmate. She married him for the money, but it turned to "true love" and they remarried, "for love" the second time around.

Starr Manning

Téa's adorable stepdaughter, who affectionately calls her stepmommy..... "Tee".

Roseanne Delgado

Téa's niece, initially came to town holding a grudge against Téa for her mother's death, but they have since mended their differences.

Moose Manning

Todd's pet parrot. Moose and Téa didn't get along too well... but ummm, are "family" just the same (lol)!

*FRIENDS*

Carlotta Vega

Téa's longtime family friend and "mother figure". She brought Téa to Llanview to help defend son, Antonio

Rachel Gannon

Téa's best friend and former roommate. Rachel and Téa commiserate over guys woes, counsel each other and are always there for each other.

Andrew Carpenter

One of Téa's closest friends. They bonded over being left by their lovers Cassie and Kevin. Andrew is always ready to offer Téa advice. Téa and Andrew have slept together once.

*FOES*

Cassie Carpenter Buchanan

Andrew Carpenter's and Kevin Buchanan's ex-wife. No love lost between these two. Téa had a sexual affair with Kevin Buchanan, the man who Cassie eventually left Andrew to marry.

Blair Daimler Cramer

The ex-wife of Todd Manning and Starr's mother, resents the time that Téa spent with Starr. Téa once provoked Blair to such an extent that Blair pushed her out a two-story window.

Kelly Cramer

Kelly approached Téa for 'hypothetical' legal advice. Their relationship hit a snag when Téa married cousin Blair's ex-hubby, Todd. These two have had a couple of fights; luckily for Téa, no windows were involved!

Dorian Lord Hayes

Matriarch of the Cramer clan. Téa and Dorian had some heated confrontations during the custody battle for Starr (as Blair lay in a coma) and more recently (in her role as ADA), Téa prosecuted Dorian for Jessica's hit-and-run accident.

Nora Hanen Gannon Buchanan

Llanview's legal ace. Téa served as her co-counsel on Antonio's case. Neither woman has been able to stand the sight of the other since Téa asked to be Nora's Junior partner, though Nora did serve as Téa's divorce attorney.

*CLIENTS*

Antonio Vega

Carlotta's oldest son, Téa's first client in Llanview. Although there was a longstanding bond between their families, their relationship was very antagonistic.

Eli Trager

Eli ripped off the DA's bike, but Téa was able to get the charges dropped against the kid.

Alex Olanov Hesser

Todd Manning hired Téa to defend Alex during her trial for the murder of Carlo Hesser and the kidnapping of Andy Harrison.

Bo Buchanan

When Bo was accused of murdering Georgie Phillips, Téa served on his defense team, despite Todd's objections and the fact that Todd was working to prove Bo's guilt.

*Téa Delgado Manning* *Family, Friends, Foes & Clients*
